organ wales and a doctor of engineering degree from carleton university in may  he was appointed an officer of the order of the british empire matthews is also chairman of a number of hightechnology companies including crosskeys west end systems timestep televittese castleton systems starvision multimedia corporation and tundra semiconductor he is also chairman of the uk company celtic inns recommended your friends are reading cairine reay wilson  jim pattison  blakeman welch  the deportation of the acadians  new france  battle of vimy ridge  you must be logged in to post a comment matthews terence h  all documents  contracts agreements deals legal docs home contracts all contracts business compensation corporate employment fee agreements financials financing insurance leasing legal licensing loans ma miscellany plans purchase  sale real estate securities services companies a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z  industries all industries biotechnology  drugs capital goods commodities construction consumer energy financial healthcare insurance miscellany real estate retail services technology transportation utilities subscriptions subscriptions cancellations faqs support about us contact us faqs receipts services signin homecompanies librarymatthews terence h  matthews terence h by category corporatefinancinglegalmiscellany all categories view documenttitledaterelated entities full doc termination agreement     matthews terence h previewfull doc registration rights agreement     matthews terence h full doc transfer agreement     matthews terence h previewfull doc transfer agreement     matthews terence h    the consus group llc      privacy policy      terms of service terence h matthews  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in terence h matthews chairman of the board at counterpath corporation view full profile are you terence h matthews claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view 