ration an investment group with offices in the united kingdom and canada that invests in a broad range of nextgeneration technology companies real estate and hotels and resorts in addition dr matthews is currently chairman or serves on the board of directors of a number of high technology companies including counterpath corporation prontoforms corporation solace systems inc and benbria corporation dr matthews holds an honors degree in electronics from the university of wales swansea and is a fellow of the institute of electrical engineers and of the royal academy of engineering he has been awarded honorary doctorates by several universities including the university of wales glamorgan and swansea and carleton university in ottawa in  he was appointed an officer of the order of the british empire and in the  queens birthday honours he was awarded a knighthood in  he was appointed patron of the cancer stem cell research institute at cardiff university source mitel networks corporation on    sign up for equilar atlas and view terence h matthewss full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like terence h matthews more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in terence h matthewss network and community follow changes in terence h matthewss employment and moneyinmotion connect with terence h matthews through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example terence h matthews terence h matthewss connections  sign up now to view terence h matthewss  connections » peter allen former president  ceo and board member dragonwave inc john a macdonald former board member rogers communications inc david farrar former founder  vp operations dragonwave inc philip b keenan former executive vice president sales service and marketing americas mitel networks corporation alvaro pombo former president and chief executive officer prontoforms steven e 